00:00:11.266 --> 00:00:15.176
What is Sahajyog?

00:00:15.501 --> 00:00:17.000
Sahajyog!

00:00:17.744 --> 00:00:25.630
'Saha' means with you and 'ja 'means born.

00:00:25.655 --> 00:00:38.780
'Yog' means your attention's union with

00:00:41.073 --> 00:00:45.732
God 's power of love that is spread all around.

00:00:45.763 --> 00:00:49.299
This occurance itself is called 'yog'.

00:00:52.528 --> 00:00:55.881
This is the birth right of every human being.

00:00:56.421 --> 00:01:06.143
To get it , as the other meaning of 'Sahaj" is easy, spontanious.

00:01:07.649 --> 00:01:12.291
For this, there is proper arrangement within us.

00:01:13.165 --> 00:01:18.486
There is nobody within whom there is no such arrangement

00:01:18.511 --> 00:01:22.010
means within your triangular bone

00:01:22.035 --> 00:01:25.334
which is called 'Sacrum' in English language

00:01:25.360 --> 00:01:34.567
It means that Greeks knew that

00:01:34.686 --> 00:01:43.390
the traingular bone is sacred, means it is pure.

00:01:43.557 --> 00:01:47.034
That is why its name is 'Sacrum' since eternity.

00:01:48.042 --> 00:01:52.561
Now this bone

00:01:52.586 --> 00:01:54.331
In this traingular bone

00:01:55.582 --> 00:01:59.934
three and half circles

00:01:59.959 --> 00:02:06.192
the power that is inherent in it, is called Kundalini in Sanskrit.

00:02:08.090 --> 00:02:16.130
Within us God has bestowed three more powers too.

00:02:20.369 --> 00:02:27.644
One of those powers is that we desire.

00:02:28.030 --> 00:02:32.017
Our power of desire, our everyday work of the power of desire.

00:02:32.271 --> 00:02:35.751
And another is our power of action.

00:02:35.776 --> 00:02:41.920
This nourishes our sympathetic nervous system.

00:02:44.474 --> 00:02:48.985
Its nourishment depends upon these two chakras.

00:02:50.089 --> 00:02:55.336
First power, with the help of which we desire

00:02:55.361 --> 00:03:04.180
the channel through which that power is broadcasted

00:03:04.205 --> 00:03:07.725
is called Ida Nadi.

00:03:09.014 --> 00:03:12.921
And the other power that gets activated

00:03:12.946 --> 00:03:15.655
they do the work for the desire they have

00:03:16.394 --> 00:03:21.257
with their existence and their body

00:03:21.282 --> 00:03:26.197
that power which we can say is

00:03:26.229 --> 00:03:30.254
our right sympathetic nervous system.

00:03:30.357 --> 00:03:33.700
But its name is Pingala Nadi.

00:03:33.725 --> 00:03:36.673
In this way , there are two channels within us.

00:03:36.933 --> 00:03:39.980
Ida and Pingla Nadi.

00:03:40.175 --> 00:03:44.300
Apart from these there is third channel within us.

00:03:44.325 --> 00:03:47.000
This is called Sushumna, which is in the center

00:03:47.025 --> 00:03:48.171
is called MADHYA MARG.

00:03:48.196 --> 00:03:55.129
Both these powers come from left and right and join like this.

00:03:55.154 --> 00:03:57.645
And in the center a chakra is made

00:03:57.670 --> 00:03:59.728
(Showing with HER hands)

00:04:01.152 --> 00:04:05.307
within the central chakras

00:04:09.476 --> 00:04:15.709
our physical, mental, intellectual, cultural

00:04:16.497 --> 00:04:24.098
even our spiritual, all progress is settled.

00:04:24.828 --> 00:04:26.495
When these chakras

00:04:27.339 --> 00:04:36.553
get damaged on some account, or their power recedes and is destroyed

00:04:36.622 --> 00:04:40.354
