00:58:42.927 --> 00:58:45.564
Wherever you go, Dharma means to quarrell.

00:58:45.819 --> 00:58:47.556
There will be a dispute between Shias and Sunis

00:58:47.715 --> 00:58:49.107
How can that be?

00:58:49.132 --> 00:58:52.384
If dharma is one, why your disputes?

00:58:53.809 --> 00:58:58.445
Now we should think that there is some fault in it.

00:58:58.561 --> 00:58:59.224
That in this way

00:58:59.249 --> 00:59:03.201
we are fighting in the name of Dharma, in the name of God

00:59:04.424 --> 00:59:07.292
How is it possible? It is impossible.

00:59:07.372 --> 00:59:09.784
It means that we are away from God.

00:59:10.038 --> 00:59:14.548
We are not closer to God. If a human being understands this

00:59:14.573 --> 00:59:17.446
God's work is to give love

00:59:17.471 --> 00:59:19.564
have to bring together everybody

00:59:19.589 --> 00:59:21.603
have to essemble everybody in Samashti (COLLECTIVITY).

00:59:21.628 --> 00:59:23.360
All these disputes will be over.

00:59:23.630 --> 00:59:25.058
But it cannot be with the help of wisdom

00:59:25.344 --> 00:59:27.549
The work done by wisdom

00:59:27.574 --> 00:59:31.371
goes on and on and on  from here with thoughts

00:59:31.396 --> 00:59:32.587
and then returns back.

00:59:32.612 --> 00:59:36.333
There is no truth in it. What's the basis to support it?

00:59:36.419 --> 00:59:40.074
But the thought of Atma is spread all over.

00:59:41.582 --> 00:59:43.247
Now it is going on spreading.

00:59:43.272 --> 00:59:46.641
It doesn't have any apprehension of falling down.

00:59:47.611 --> 00:59:50.632
Because of this we see that the Dharma

00:59:50.657 --> 00:59:52.765
people have made out of their minds,

00:59:52.790 --> 00:59:55.823
one should say, made a system of it

00:59:55.848 --> 00:59:58.117
and made its repurcussions.

00:59:58.156 --> 01:00:01.484
That has caused notions about Dharma

01:00:01.603 --> 01:00:03.623
and has twisted and returned back again.

01:00:03.648 --> 01:00:05.853
It is called 'Bhoomrang' in English.

01:00:05.878 --> 01:00:08.489
In this way it has mesmerrised a human being.

01:00:09.798 --> 01:00:11.849
But now they are fighting and quarrelling.

01:00:12.350 --> 01:00:14.976
It should not be so in our country.

01:00:15.155 --> 01:00:17.986
Don't know how many saints and sages must have been here

01:00:18.011 --> 01:00:22.240
and never did any saint talk like this.

01:00:23.602 --> 01:00:29.867
Some time there were Brahmins, there were Shudras too

01:00:29.892 --> 01:00:32.131
and there were many types of casts as well.

01:00:32.425 --> 01:00:38.651
But one saint respects another saint  with love.

01:00:38.676 --> 01:00:40.962
It can happen only when you are a real saint.

01:00:42.950 --> 01:00:45.484
Then you will have respect towards another person

01:00:45.588 --> 01:00:47.620
then your questions will be over.

01:00:47.645 --> 01:00:51.985
If I will say a little bit at the end

01:00:52.010 --> 01:00:56.260
in Maharashtra there was a poet named Nam Dev

01:00:56.285 --> 01:00:59.148
whom Guru Nanak also recognised

01:00:59.958 --> 01:01:05.090
and another  saint was a potter.

01:01:06.762 --> 01:01:09.694
Namdev went to meet him.

01:01:11.246 --> 01:01:12.599
He went to see him.

01:01:12.624 --> 01:01:15.019
On seeing him, he stood up immediately.

01:01:15.044 --> 01:01:17.424
In Marathi he said

01:01:17.786 --> 01:01:20.296
NIRGUNA CHA BETI ALO SAGUNA SANGHEY

01:01:20.321 --> 01:01:23.808
I had come to see NIRGUNA in you, Chaitanya in you

01:01:23.967 --> 01:01:24.967
SAGUNA is standing in front of me.

01:01:25.860 --> 01:01:28.891
One saint is saying to another saint.

01:01:28.939 --> 01:01:31.971
saints have always respected saints.

01:01:31.996 --> 01:01:34.026
Among Muslims those who are Sufis

01:01:34.074 --> 01:01:40.323
Hazrat Muhammad Nizamudin Sahab, then Khusro Sahab

01:01:40.616 --> 01:01:41.921
Mouddin Sahab

01:01:41.946 --> 01:01:43.457
In this way everywhere

01:01:43.560 --> 01:01:47.417
I have seen Sufis

01:01:48.127 --> 01:01:53.965
they are in Erussia and are in Turkey.

01:01:53.990 --> 01:01:56.536
And in Turkey there were some old Sufis.

01:01:56.561 --> 01:02:03.752
They said that Shri Mataji's work is greater than that of Fatima B.

01:02:04.334 --> 01:02:05.428
Now they will recognise ME.

01:02:05.453 --> 01:02:08.499
Now they are no more in this world but his disciples recognise ME.

01:02:08.524 --> 01:02:10.546
In this way, in every family

01:02:10.821 --> 01:02:13.737
such were saints and sages, in every dharma.

01:02:13.762 --> 01:02:15.416
there was no such dharma.

01:02:15.631 --> 01:02:17.650
And they all think that

01:02:18.063 --> 01:02:25.653
all the religions are the out come of one tree of spiritualism.

01:02:26.194 --> 01:02:27.593
And they don't have this question

01:02:27.618 --> 01:02:31.033
because we are in darkness and don't know

01:02:31.058 --> 01:02:34.641
and  we quarrell in this darkness, in this ignorance.

01:02:34.666 --> 01:02:38.172
This problem  instantly gets over in Sahajyoga

01:02:38.355 --> 01:02:42.572
Not only this if the dispute of various Dharmas is over

01:02:42.819 --> 01:02:43.819
but the countries

01:02:45.090 --> 01:02:49.077
the countries which once were our enemies

01:02:49.102 --> 01:02:51.732
are friendly in Sahajyoga today.

01:02:51.979 --> 01:02:56.253
Everywhere Iranians, Pakistanis

01:02:56.278 --> 01:02:58.241
poeple have come from far off countries

01:02:58.384 --> 01:03:00.565
I am so surprised to find

01:03:00.590 --> 01:03:01.701
how much they have progressed

01:03:01.948 --> 01:03:04.197
and how they have evolved to this stage.

01:03:04.428 --> 01:03:08.133
In this way what we call national integration

01:03:08.405 --> 01:03:10.813
it cannot be done by force.

01:03:11.345 --> 01:03:14.084
It cannot be done by making to understand or by giving lectures.

01:03:14.109 --> 01:03:17.271
With the help of  inner transformation, it takes place on its own.

01:03:17.507 --> 01:03:22.200
No need to say anything!
